    "title": "Job Opening Category Manager at Mamaearth Capital India",
    "description": "Mamaearth Capital India, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Category Manager for our Delhi operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Mamaearth Capital India:\nMamaearth Capital India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Referral bonus program\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Delhi, Delhi, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Mamaearth Capital India!",
